{"title":"已解决-Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现","uid":"b7299ee111bc51c458f38e9a92cd9083","slug":"bug复现","date":"2023-12-12T06:17:43.000Z","updated":"2023-12-12T06:27:17.958Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/bug复现.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"已解决-Hexo-Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现\"><a href=\"#已解决-Hexo-Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"[已解决]Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现\"></a>[已解决]Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现</h1><blockquote>\n<p>很好，通过发布这篇文章，我有发现了，yaml语法里面不能有<code>[]</code>，要不然hexo g的时候会报错，哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈，好你的</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"一、本地搜索无法使用\"><a href=\"#一、本地搜索无法使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、本地搜索无法使用\"></a>一、本地搜索无法使用</h2><p>如图，一直在转圈圈</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121409748.png\" alt=\"image-20231212140912128\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-1-F12查看\"><a href=\"#1-1-F12查看\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.1 F12查看\"></a>1.1 F12查看</h3><p><strong>发现状态为200，那么恭喜你，参考下文即可顺利解决问题</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121410703.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141000256\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-2-访问search-xml\"><a href=\"#1-2-访问search-xml\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.2 访问search.xml\"></a>1.2 访问search.xml</h3><p>显示这里，说明文章里面有些字符，无法识别</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121410237.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141045168\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-3-找到问题文章\"><a href=\"#1-3-找到问题文章\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.3 找到问题文章\"></a>1.3 找到问题文章</h3><p>网页拉倒最下面，确定文章关键字，如果文章数量太多，无法人为找到，本地打开search.xml文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121412383.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141205290\"></p>\n<p>本地搜索后，可以确定问题文章</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121413461.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141330341\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-4-解决字符问题\"><a href=\"#1-4-解决字符问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.4 解决字符问题\"></a>1.4 解决字符问题</h3><p>根据文件检索，定位。最终确定问题出现在这里</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121414635.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141423496\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>放入代码块范围</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121415703.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141509628\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-5-大功告成\"><a href=\"#1-5-大功告成\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.5 大功告成\"></a>1.5 大功告成</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121415324.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141533804\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-6-重新部署发布即可\"><a href=\"#1-6-重新部署发布即可\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.6 重新部署发布即可\"></a>1.6 重新部署发布即可</h3><p>在网页端，也能正常检索了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121418506.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141811745\"></p>\n","text":"[已解决]Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现 很好，通过发布这篇文章，我有发现了，yaml语法里面不能有[]，要不然hexo g的时候会报错...","permalink":"/post/bug复现","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":347,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B7%B2%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3-Hexo-Fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8bug%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">[已解决]Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、本地搜索无法使用</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-1-F12%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.1 F12查看</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-2-%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AEsearch-xml\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.2 访问search.xml</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><